    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014it's been well-maintained and still has plenty of adventures left in it! Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is super reliable and ready for its next home. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
