    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of pride in ownership, presenting in excellent shape for its age. The exterior maintains a lustrous finish with only the slightest evidence of careful road use, and the interior is remarkably clean, featuring well-preserved upholstery and a smoke-free cabin. Mechanically, it is turn-key ready; the engine is responsive, the gear shifts are seamless, and the braking is firm and reliable. We have kept up with all scheduled maintenance, and every feature\u2014from the cold A/C to the premium sound system\u2014works exactly as it should. It offers a smooth, confident driving experience that feels tight and well-composed on the road.",
      "price": 34500.0,
