    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies. Power is delivered via a 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings to maintain optimal suspension geometry under lateral load. Recent preventative maintenance includes a VANOS system overhaul and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the valvetrain and bottom end are track-ready. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains tight and responsive, offering the visceral feedback only a naturally aspirated M-car can provide.",
